    <lb n="12"/>κ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">αὶ</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἱερεί</unclear>ων ὧν δέ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δ</unclear>ωκεν Κρίτωνι. 

